# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CODEOWNERS — automatic PR reviewers
# Requires branch protection rule: "Require review from Code Owners"
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Default: backend team reviews everything
*                                       @ecom360/backend

# CI/CD changes need DevOps review
.github/                                @ecom360/devops @ecom360/backend
Dockerfile                              @ecom360/devops
docker-compose*.yml                     @ecom360/devops

# Database migrations need DBA/senior review
src/main/resources/db/migration/        @ecom360/backend-senior

# Security config needs security review
**/security/                            @ecom360/backend-senior
**/SecurityConfig*                      @ecom360/backend-senior
